node.text:
Scenes from Today's video!
Check out😛

I look pretty🙈
Also, I found this new hobby during the time when I was not feeling like doing anything.

Best way to cope up with these difficult times is to do something that calms your mind be it painting, sleeping, singing, meditating, dancing or anything.

Art is therapy, and we all need it!

Keep yourself engaged in something or other tto keep urself away from all the negativity.
I hope you all stay strong and give your 100%
😊

#guitar🎸 #yougogirl #stayhomesafe #keephustlin

node.text:
The ME-ME Moment😂

This was the best example of "Taking First step is the most difficult part"
I will explain howw...

The journey to get to the highest point was scary...like "bilkul dhak dhak hora thaa" And then after getting there, the instructor said... JUMP😱

It will be a lie if I say uss time meri faatii nhi😐..

Eyes closed
Taking the leap of faith
Gooo for itttt Khushboooo

Andddd
The journey after that.....😍

It was all totally worth ittt💙✨
(The last pic💚)

The first step is the scariest and most Important one✨

#daarkeaagejeethai
#mondaythoughts
#leapoffaith #paraglidinggirls #adventureislife
#goforitgirl
